e": "2025-04-28T21:51:12.246329"}}}]}, "id": "a9295e81-0d3b-45c8-9ec6-f2c824dc8072", "updated_at": {"value": "2025-04-28T21:51:12.246334"}}}]}, "id": "55f57414-a5e8-44a8-b1a5-4231f94efca5", "updated_at": {"value": "2025-04-28T21:51:12.246338"}}}, {"description": "The giant casts one of the following spells, requiring no Material components and using Wisdom as the spellcasting ability (spell save DC 18):\nAt will: Detect Magic, Light\n\n1/day each: Control Weather", "id": -1, "isLegendary": false, "monsterId": -1, "name": "Spellcasting", "type": "NONE"}]}, "bonus_actions": {"value": []}, "reactions": {"value": []}, "legendary_actions": {"value": []}, "spells": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Detect Magic"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_1"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_divination"}, "ritual": {"value": true}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "Self (30-foot radius)"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 10 minutes"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "description": {"value": "For the duration, you sense the presence of magical effects within 30 feet of yourself. If you sense such effects, you can take the Magic action to see a faint aura around any visible creature or object in the area that bears the magic, and if an effect was created by a spell, you learn the spell's school of magic.\n\nThe spell is blocked by 1 foot of stone, dirt, or wood; 1 inch of metal; or a thin sheet of lead"}, "classes": {"value": ["bard", "cleric", "druid", "paladin", "ranger", "sorcerer", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard", "warlock"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.608985"}, "id": "detect_magic"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Light"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_evocation"}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "Touch"}, "duration": {"value": "1 hour"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a firefly or phosphorescent moss"}, "description": {"value": "You touch one Large or smaller object that isn't being worn or carried by someone else. Until the spell ends, the object sheds Bright Light in a 20-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 20 feet. The light can be colored as you like.\n\nCovering the object with something opaque blocks the light. The spell ends if you cast it again"}, "classes": {"value": ["bard", "cleric", "sorcerer", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.617630"}, "id": "light"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Control Weather"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_8"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_transmutation"}, "casting_time": {"value": "10 minutes"}, "range": {"value": "Self (5-mile radius)"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 8 hours"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "burning incense"}, "description": {"value": "You take control of the weather within 5 miles of you for the duration. You must be outdoors to cast this spell. Moving to a place where you don't have a clear path to the sky ends the spell early.\n\nWhen you cast the spell, you change the current weather conditions, which are determined by the GM based on the climate and season. You can change precipitation, temperature, and wind. It takes 1d4 x 10 minutes for the new conditions to take effect. Once they do so, you can change the conditions again. When the spell ends, the weather gradually returns to normal.\n\nWhen you change the weather conditions, find a current condition on the following tables and change its stage by one, up or down. When changing the wind, you can change its direction.\n\nPrecipitation:\n\nStage 1 - Clear\nStage 2 - Light clouds\nStage 3 - Overcast or ground fog\nStage 4 - Rain, hail, or snow\nStage 5 - Torrential rain, driving hail, or blizzard\n\nTemperature:\n\nStage 1 - Heat wave\nStage 2 - Hot\nStage 3 - Warm\nStage 4 - Cool\nStage 5 - Cold\nStage 6 - Arctic cold\n\nWind:\n\nStage 1 - Calm\nStage 2 - Moderate wind\nStage 3 - Strong wind\nStage 4 - Gale\nStage 5 - Storm"}, "classes": {"value": ["cleric", "druid", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.639053"}, "id": "control_weather"}}]}, "habitat": {"value": ["coastal", "underwater"]}, "treasure": {"value": ["armaments"]}, "updated_at": {"value": "2025-04-28T21:51:12.246511"}}}